N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 166.2 - "cull" potatoes identification

State Regulations

Any lot of "cull" potatoes, regardless of place of origin, when sold or offered for sale in this State shall be definitely represented as
cull potatoes. Every invoice rendered in connection with the sale of cull
potatoes shall describe the potatoes as "cull" potatoes. Notes
